345
00:22:25,752 --> 00:22:26,786
<font color=#FFFF00>Hai, Sang Goo.</font>

346
00:22:34,294 --> 00:22:36,696
<font color=#FFFF00>Tangkap dia!</font>

347
00:22:40,867 --> 00:22:42,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang jika aku
