356
00:23:07,994 --> 00:23:08,995
<font color=#FFFF00>Berangkat!</font>

357
00:23:10,163 --> 00:23:11,164
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat!</font>

358
00:23:30,450 --> 00:23:31,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau belum pernah kesini, 'kan?</font>

359
00:23:34,487 --> 00:23:36,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah kantornya...</font>

360
00:23:36,256 --> 00:23:38,658
<font color=#FFFF00>....Il Hwan dulu saat dia memulai usaha
Firma Hukum Taebaek 30 tahun yang lalu.</font>

361
00:23:40,994 --> 00:23:42,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Il Hwan...</font>

362
00:23:42,796 --> 00:23:45,065
<font color=#FFFF00>...belum tahu kalau aku masih
