363
00:23:45,365 --> 00:23:46,366
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

364
00:23:47,100 --> 00:23:49,803
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, Baek Sang Goo.../
Dia memihak Dong Joon, 'kan?</font>

365
00:23:51,338 --> 00:23:52,572
<font color=#FFFF00>Gawat ini.</font>

366
00:23:53,506 --> 00:23:56,176
<font color=#FFFF00>Jung Il. Ini akan berakhir
beberapa hari lagi.</font>

367
00:23:57,410 --> 00:23:59,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Kartu tersembunyinya
masih ada di aku.</font>

368
00:24:01,081 --> 00:24:02,082
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

369
00:24:14,794 --> 00:24:15,795
<font color=#FFFF00>Duduklah.</font>

370
00:24:19,532 --> 00:24:21,768
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda mengirim ini ke rumahku.</font>

371
00:24:22,168 --> 00:24:23,803
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan aku menelepon Anda
