476
00:30:22,795 --> 00:30:24,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka bisa mencari
banyak alasan.</font>

477
00:30:24,797 --> 00:30:26,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus membuktikan kalau
