479
00:30:30,236 --> 00:30:31,537
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi begini garis besarnya.</font>

480
00:30:32,438 --> 00:30:35,408
<font color=#FFFF00>Choi Soo Yun menyaksikan kejadian dan
