491
00:31:09,675 --> 00:31:11,077
<font color=#FFFF00>Kabarnya kau punya banyak kenangan.</font>

492
00:31:13,713 --> 00:31:15,915
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan saatnya
perdebatan sepasang kekasih.</font>

493
00:31:27,360 --> 00:31:28,694
<font color=#FFFF00>Dulu saat kita di Amerika...,</font>

494
00:31:29,896 --> 00:31:32,098
