498
00:31:42,375 --> 00:31:46,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Baek Sang Goo sudah memihak Lee Dong Joon.</font>

499
00:31:47,113 --> 00:31:49,215
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika mereka membuktikan
